Subject: [PATCH] Add Redis-backed rate limiting to sensitive API endpoints

- New src/lib/api/rate-limit.ts: fixed-window limiter on existing Upstash
  Redis (no new dependency), fail-open on Redis errors, 429 + Retry-After.
- Apply to wallet import, analyzer run, and telegram link-token endpoints.
- Adds RATE_LIMITS presets for reuse across remaining routes.
